### create operation — any endpoint writes to the operations table,
### which the sync-source-connector captures from the WAL and forwards to critical_db
POST http://localhost:8080/operations/v1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "b2000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "assetId": "07261f3e-2447-41a5-84e2-87811e535b2f",
  "side": "BUY",
  "quantity": 2,
  "price": 80000
}

### operations in operations-service (source)
GET http://localhost:8080/operations/account/b2000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### operations synced into critical_db by the JDBC Sink connector
### Should reflect the same rows as the source above.
GET http://localhost:8081/operations
